Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/redbluff/dotvim.git ~/.vim
    git clone git://github.com/redbluff/dotvim.git vimfiles (windows)

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

    mklink _vimrc vimfiles\vimrc
    mklink _gvimrc vimfiles\gvimrc  (windows)

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update

To add a submodule...

    git submodule add 'the submodule' bundle/submodule
    
To update the submodules to latest versions..
    git submodule foreach git pull origin/master
    or can indivually update...

